<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.1.8">
<l>cēya ṉaṇiyaṉ ciṟiyaṉ periya ṉeṉpa tucilarp pēcak kēṭṭirun</l>
<l>tēveṉ ṉeñcamaṉ pāye ṉakkoṉṟu collātē</l>
<l>vēykaḷ niṉṟuveṇ mutta mēcori vēṅka ṭamalai kōyil mēviya</l>
<l>vāyar nāyakaṟ kiṉṟa ṭimaittoḻil pūṇṭāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My companion heart, having heard when a few said</l>
<l>That he is near, he is far, he is little, [and] he is huge,</l>
<l rend="indent">without saying anything to me,</l>
<l>Today you assumed the duty of service to the lord of the herders</l>
<l>Who dwells [in] the temple on Vēṅkaṭa mountain</l>
<l rend="indent">where white pearls pour from bamboo.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
